[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"prije 6 mjeseci","text":"Imali smo fondue s juhom i OBOŽAVALI smo salatu i povrće. Meso je meso kuhano u juhi pa nije bilo previše uzbudljivo. Probao bih nešto drugo i manje turističko. “Francuski” preljev bio je fantastičan! Podsjetio nas je Amerikance na pojednostavljeni ranch dressing, ali definitivno nije bio ranch dressing!

Objekt je noviji od svega što smo probali na ovom putovanju. Podsjeća na hotel tipa "konvencijskog" centra u Americi. Osoblje je bilo divno i mješavina orašastih plodova u baru svakako je vrijedna probe!","time":1736842377,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"prije 2 mjeseca","text":"Hrana je jednostavno odlična. Imala sam goveđu juhu s palačinkama, govedinu na vrućim kamenjima koju morate sami peći, brokulu. Atmosfera je lijepa, pogledi fantastični, konobari profesionalni.","time":1747596736,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"prije godinu dana","text":"Bila sam tamo dva puta, prvi put je sve prošlo dobro, hrana je bila ukusna, preporučujem goveđi gulaš s gljivama eierschwammerl :)
Međutim, drugi put je bilo nekoliko razočaranja - tjestenina je bila gotovo hladna, ramen juha je bila izuzetno slana, jedva sam je mogla pojesti i ne može se usporediti s pravim ramenom po dubini okusa. Za desert smo imali izbor pakiranih čaša sladoleda koje su, nažalost, bile stare i nisu bile dobre pa smo ih vratili. Usluga je izuzetno ljubazna i prijateljska, ugodna atmosfera. Sve u svemu, ponešto bi se moglo poboljšati, ali sigurno ćemo se vratiti još jednom.","time":1702802723,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"prije godinu dana","text":"Restoran ima vrlo ugodan interijer i imali smo sreće da jedemo u mirnu srijedu navečer.

Naručili smo edamame, Caesar salatu, šnicle i ramen juhu. Sve je bilo vrlo ukusno, jedino je porcija ramen juhe bila nedovoljna za glavno jelo. A krumpir uz šniclu bio je malo bezukusan.

Naš konobar bio je vrlo pažljiv i ljubazan.

Odlična večer i sjajno mjesto za večeru s ukusnom hranom!","time":1711193544,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"prije godinu dana","text":"Vrlo ugodan ručak na nevjerojatnom mjestu.
Hrana je bila zaista dobra i vrijedna cijene, atmosfera je bila vrlo sugestivna, osobito zahvaljujući izvrsnom pogledu s velikih prozora na krajolik.","time":1702202414,"translated":false}]

[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"vor 6 Monaten","text":"Wir hatten die Brühe Fondue und LIEBTEN den Salat und das Gemüse. Fleisch ist Fleisch, das in Brühe gegart wird, daher war es nicht allzu aufregend. Ich würde etwas anderes und weniger touristisches probieren. Das „französische“ Dressing war fantastisch! Es erinnerte uns Amerikaner an ein vereinfachtes Ranch-Dressing, aber definitiv kein Ranch-Dressing!

Die Einrichtung ist neuer als alles, was wir auf dieser Reise ausprobiert haben. Erinnert an ein „Kongress“-Zentrum-Hotel in den USA. Das Personal war liebenswürdig und die Nussmischung an der Bar ist ein Muss!","time":1736842377,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"vor 2 Monaten","text":"Das Essen ist einfach großartig. Hatte Rinderbrühe mit Pfannkuchen, Rindfleisch auf heißen Steinen, das man selbst zubereiten muss, Brokkoli. Die Atmosphäre ist schön, die Aussichten großartig, die Kellner professionell.","time":1747596736,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"vor einem Jahr","text":"War dort 2 Mal, beim ersten Mal lief alles gut, das Essen war köstlich, das Eierschwammerlgulasch ist ein Muss :)
Allerdings gab es beim zweiten Mal ein paar Enttäuschungen - das Pastagericht wurde fast kalt serviert, die Ramensuppe war extrem salzig, konnte sie kaum essen und kann in Sachen Geschmacksintensität nicht wirklich mit einer wirklichen Ramen vergleichen. Zum Dessert gab es die Wahl zwischen einem verpackten Becher Eiscreme, der leider alt und nicht gut war, sodass wir ihn zurückgegeben haben. Der Service ist extrem nett und freundlich, angenehme Atmosphäre. Insgesamt könnten einige Kleinigkeiten verbessert werden, aber wir werden sicherlich wiederkommen, um einen weiteren Versuch zu wagen.","time":1702802723,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"vor einem Jahr","text":"Das Restaurant hat ein sehr gemütliches Interieur und wir hatten das Glück, an einem ruhigen Mittwochabend zu essen.

Wir bestellten Edamame, Caesarsalat, Schnitzel und Ramensuppe.
Alles war sehr lecker, nur die Portion der Ramensuppe war nicht ausreichend als Hauptgericht. Und die Kartoffeln zum Schnitzel waren etwas geschmacklos.

Unser Kellner war sehr aufmerksam und freundlich.

Ein guter Abend und ein großartiger Ort für ein Abendessen mit leckerem Essen!","time":1711193544,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"vor einem Jahr","text":"Sehr angenehmes Mittagessen an einem großartigen Ort. Das Essen war wirklich gut und den Preis wert, die Atmosphäre war sehr stimmungsvoll, insbesondere dank des großartigen Ausblicks aus den großen Fenstern auf die Landschaft.","time":1702202414,"translated":false}]

[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"6 months ago","text":"We had the broth fondue and LOVED the salad and veggies.  Meat is meat cooked in broth so it was not too exciting. I would try something else and less touristy. The “French” dressing was fantastic! It reminded us Americans of a simplified ranch dressing, but definitely not ranch dressing!

The facility is newer than everything else we have tried on this trip. Reminiscent of a “convention” center type hotel in the states.  Staff was lovely and the nut mix at the bar is a must try!","time":1736842377,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"2 months ago","text":"The food is just great. Had beef broth with pancakes, beef on hot stones you have to bake yourself, brokoli. The atmosphere is nice, the views great, waiters professional.","time":1747596736,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"a year ago","text":"Went there 2 times, first time everything went well, food was delicious, eierschwammerl goulash is a must try :)
However second time there were a few let downs - pasta dish was served almost cold, ramen soup was extremely salty, couldn’t hardly eat it and can’t really compare to an actual ramen in depth of flavor. For dessert there was a choice of packaged cup of ice cream which, unfortunately, was old and not good so we returned it back. Service is extremely nice and friendly, pleasant atmosphere. Overall, a little bits and pieces could be improved but we’ll certainly come back again for another try.","time":1702802723,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"a year ago","text":"The restaurant has a very cozy interior design and we were lucky to eat on a quiet Wednesday evening.

We ordered Edamame, Caesar salad, Schnitzel and Ramen soup.
Everything was very delicious, just the portion of the Ramen soup was not enough for a main course. And the potatoes to the Schnitzel were a little tasteless.

Our waiter was very attentive and friendly.

A good evening and great place for a dinner with delicious food!","time":1711193544,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"a year ago","text":"Very pleasant lunch in an awesome place.
The food was really good and worth the price, the atmosphere was really suggestive and especially thanks to the great view from the big windows of the landscape.","time":1702202414,"translated":false}]

[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"6 mesi fa","text":"Abbiamo provato la fonduta di brodo e abbiamo ADORATO l'insalata e le verdure. La carne è carne cotta nel brodo, quindi non era troppo eccitante. Proverei qualcos'altro e meno turistico. Il condimento "francese" era fantastico! Ci ha ricordato una versione semplificata del ranch dressing americano, ma decisamente non un ranch dressing!

La struttura è più nuova rispetto a tutto il resto che abbiamo provato in questo viaggio. Ricorda un hotel del tipo "centro congressi" negli Stati Uniti. Il personale era adorabile e il mix di noci al bar è assolutamente da provare!","time":1736842377,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"2 mesi fa","text":"Il cibo è semplicemente fantastico. Abbiamo avuto il brodo di manzo con frittelle, carne di manzo su pietre calde che devi cuocere tu stesso, broccoli. L'atmosfera è piacevole, le vedute sono grandiose, i camerieri professionali.","time":1747596736,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"un anno fa","text":"Ci sono andato 2 volte, la prima volta è andato tutto bene, il cibo era delizioso, il gulasch di funghi è assolutamente da provare :)
Tuttavia, la seconda volta ci sono stati alcuni inconvenienti - il piatto di pasta è stato servito quasi freddo, la zuppa di ramen era estremamente salata, a tal punto da non poterla quasi mangiare e non si può davvero confrontare con un vero ramen per profondità di sapore. Per dessert c'era la scelta di una coppa di gelato confezionata che, sfortunatamente, era vecchia e non buona, quindi l'abbiamo restituita. Il servizio è estremamente gentile e cordiale, l'atmosfera piacevole. Nel complesso, alcuni piccoli dettagli potrebbero essere migliorati ma certamente torneremo per un altro tentativo.","time":1702802723,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"un anno fa","text":"Il ristorante ha un design degli interni molto accogliente e siamo stati fortunati a mangiare in una tranquilla serata di mercoledì.

Abbiamo ordinato edamame, insalata Caesar, schnitzel e zuppa di ramen.
Tutto era molto delizioso, solo la porzione di zuppa di ramen non era sufficiente come piatto principale. E le patate dello schnitzel erano un po' insipide.

Il nostro cameriere era molto attento e amichevole.

Una buona serata e un ottimo posto per una cena con cibo delizioso!","time":1711193544,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"un anno fa","text":"Pranzo molto piacevole in un posto incredibile.
Il cibo era davvero buono e valeva il prezzo, l'atmosfera era davvero suggestiva e soprattutto grazie alla vista magnifica dalle grandi finestre sul paesaggio.","time":1702202414,"translated":false}]

[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"il y a 6 mois","text":"Nous avons pris la fondue de bouillon et ADORÉ la salade et les légumes. La viande est de la viande cuite dans le bouillon donc ce n'était pas très excitant. J'essaierais autre chose et moins touristique. La vinaigrette “française” était fantastique ! Elle nous a rappelé, à nous Américains, une vinaigrette ranch simplifiée, mais certainement pas une vinaigrette ranch !

L'établissement est plus récent que tout ce que nous avons essayé lors de ce voyage. Cela rappelle un hôtel de type centre de congrès aux États-Unis. Le personnel était charmant et le mélange de noix au bar est à essayer absolument !","time":1736842377,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"il y a 2 mois","text":"La nourriture est juste géniale. J'ai eu un bouillon de bœuf avec des crêpes, du bœuf sur des pierres chaudes que vous devez cuire vous-même, du brocoli. L'atmosphère est agréable, les vues magnifiques, les serveurs professionnels.","time":1747596736,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"il y a un an","text":"Je suis allée là deux fois, la première fois tout s'est bien passé, la nourriture était délicieuse, le goulash d'eierschwammerl est un incontournable :)
Cependant, la deuxième fois, il y a eu quelques déceptions - le plat de pâtes a été servi presque froid, la soupe ramen était extrêmement salée, j'ai eu du mal à la manger et ne peut pas vraiment la comparer à un vrai ramen en termes de profondeur de saveur. Pour le dessert, il y avait le choix d'une glace en pot emballée qui, malheureusement, était vieille et pas bonne donc nous l'avons retournée. Le service est extrêmement agréable et amical, l'atmosphère plaisante. Dans l'ensemble, quelques petits détails pourraient être améliorés mais nous reviendrons certainement pour un nouvel essai.","time":1702802723,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"il y a un an","text":"Le restaurant a un design intérieur très confortable et nous avons eu la chance de manger un soir tranquille de mercredi.

Nous avons commandé des edamame, une salade César, un schnitzel et une soupe ramen.
Tout était très délicieux, juste la portion de la soupe ramen n'était pas suffisante pour un plat principal. Et les pommes de terre avec le schnitzel étaient un peu fades.

Notre serveur était très attentionné et amical.

Une bonne soirée et un excellent endroit pour un dîner délicieux !","time":1711193544,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"il y a un an","text":"Déjeuner très agréable dans un endroit incroyable.
La nourriture était vraiment bonne et valait le prix, l'atmosphère était vraiment évocatrice, surtout grâce à la vue magnifique depuis les grandes fenêtres du paysage.","time":1702202414,"translated":true}]

[{"author_name":"javier montesquieu","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107077685752724958204/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2sFWZRCf-2RB-aeJpNmLpStbwAMSqr5EAm6JOzdfraOjcrg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":1,"relative_time_description":"5 mesi fa","text":"Ho chiesto una stanza con vista montagna e me ne hanno data una buia di fronte a un altro edificio, a circa 3 metri di distanza. La giovane e non molto simpatica ragazza alla reception mi aveva detto al momento della prenotazione che la mia stanza avrebbe dato sul parcheggio ma anche sulle montagne; non è vero. Ha anche detto che non c'erano più camere disponibili. Quando ho detto al proprietario la mattina successiva che me ne sarei andato, mi ha detto che avrebbe trovato un'altra stanza per me... Oh, ora che me ne vado ci sono camere disponibili?? 
Inoltre, la sala da pranzo era scarsamente illuminata, triste, e il servizio era terribile: nessun saluto, sorriso... il buffet di insalate era a livello di una mensa, anche se la colazione era abbastanza buona. La piscina aveva i getti rotti e la porta della spa chiusa dopo le 7 (ma non lo "sapevano") anche se affermano che è aperta fino a molto più tardi. Questo non è un hotel a 4 stelle.
